hoot-down-shade-claims-after-viral-beyonce-grammys-reaction-clip-3834440">team shut down online speculation that she threw shade at Beyoncé</a> during the latter&#39;s win for Best Country Album at the 2025 Grammys.</p><p> Bey took home the trophy for her country-inspired LP <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">&#39;Cowboy Carter&#39;</a> , and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-viral-reaction-beyonce-beating-her-best-country-win-grammys-3834057">a brief clip of Musgrave reacting soon went viral online</a> – with some viewers suggesting she was unhappy with the result.</p><p>她的团队在不久之后在一份声明中分享道：“这是一种轰动性的虚假叙事，旨在使两位才华横溢的女性艺术家互相抗衡。” “根本没有皱眉或表达。”</p><p> Beyoncé became <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-becomes-first-black-woman-to-hit-number-one-on-us-country-chart-359055">the first Black woman to reach Number One on the US country chart</a> with &#39;Texas Hold &#39;Em&#39; and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-becomes-first-black-woman-to-land-us-number-one-country-album-with-cowboy-carter-3614606">the first Black woman to score a Number One country album in the US charts</a> . She is <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-is-now-officially-the-most-nominated-artist-in-grammy-history-3811696">the most Grammy-nominated artist of all time</a> , with a total of 99 under her belt.这位歌手也赢得了所有表演中最多的格莱美奖，总体上获得了35个奖项。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-performs-new-song-shes-my-bitch-nashville-watch-3844229">Watch Kacey Musgraves perform new song &#39;She&#39;s My Bitch&#39; in Nashville</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
