ackman</a> , before a video that celebrated the lives of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-lynch">David Lynch</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/maggie-smith-dies-aged-89-3797758">Maggie Smith</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-shining-star-shelley-duvall-dies-aged-75-3774146">Shelley Duvall</a> , and others.</p><p> Jennie Garth was Doherty&#39;s co-star on <em>Beverly Hills 90210</em> , playing Kelly Taylor for the entire initial run from 1990-2000.被问到这位演员被问及她对Doherty被排除在外的事实的感觉。她回答：“那搞砸了。”当被问及学院是否应该道歉时，她说：“也许”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Jennie Garth On Shannen Doherty Oscars In Memoriam Snub <a href="https://t.co/6FO0G9pKWq">pic.twitter.com/6FO0G9pKWq</a></p><p> — TMZ (@TMZ) <a href="https://twitter.com/TMZ/status/1897337494745833751?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 5, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p></p><p> The <em>Charmed</em> star was not the only name left off the list of those remembered during the broadcast. The <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-shining-star-shelley-duvall-dies-aged-75-3774146">recently passed Michelle Trachtenberg</a> , <em>Candyman</em> actor <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/horror-icon-tony-todd-has-died-aged-69-i-will-miss-him-so-much-and-hope-he-haunts-me-once-in-a-while-3811170#:~:text=He%20was%20best%20known%20for,Living%20Dead%20and%20The%20Crow.">Tony Todd</a> , comedy legend <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/arrested-development-star-martin-mull-dies-aged-80-3771148">Martin Mull</a> , and director<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/super-size-me-director-morgan-spurlock-dies-aged-53-3759363">Morgan Spurlock</a> were among those not included.</p><p> Those names and others were, however, included in an online section on the <a href="https://aframe.oscars.org/news/in-memoriam" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oscars website</a> .</p><p> P