ding="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Billy-Nomates">Billy Nomates</a> has announced her new album &#39;Metalhorse&#39; and shared the rebellious single &#39;The Test&#39;.在下面查看。</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/billy-nomates-interview-2023-cacti-3377120">Billy Nomates: “I&#39;m a woman in the modern world, of course I&#39;m angry!”</a></strong></li></ul><p> “测试”具有低嗡嗡声的低音和明亮的钢琴插曲，这些钢琴与提名人配对”  - 真实的玛丽斯 - 强大的声音。 <em>“Hall of mirrors / I do the wall of death / and I get fearless / when it pays my rent,”</em> she sings.</p><p>这首歌是为即将发行的专辑写的第一首曲目，并在新闻稿中被描述为“过去18个月的动荡，而比利提名人仍在继续进行的令人困惑的曲目。</p><p>玛丽（Maries）将其描述为：“它正在以赔率和感觉就像是某人在另一端帮助您的工作，如果他们看到您是考验。我真的觉得当我们现场演奏时。就像，发生了一切，我简直不敢相信这就是生存。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比利提名 - 测试（官方可视化器）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BxMrKNp0Tr0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> &#39;Metalhorse&#39; is set for release on May 16 via Invada and is available for pre-order <a href="http://lnk.to/metalhorse" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .这是她2023 LP&#39;Cacti&#39;和2020年同名的首次亮相之后。</p><p>由James Trevascus制作，并在西班牙塞维利亚的Paco Loco录制，“ Metalhorse”是Maries&#39;的第一张专辑，该专辑将在一家完整乐队的工作室中制作。新闻稿承诺将其成为“ Fuller专辑”，并看到音乐家探索新的流派，例如布鲁斯，民间和钢琴驱动的安排，将她通常的Stark Punk声音转变为更卑鄙的东西。</p><p> Maries&#39; and the full band – comprised of bass player Mandy Clarke ( <a href="/artists/kt-tunstall">KT Tunstall</a> , The Go! Team) and drummer Liam Chapman (Rozi Plain, BMX Bandits) – took to the studio shortly after the passing of her father.</p><p>玛丽斯在谈到她与父亲的关系时说：“我们是如此亲密，我们的纽带是音乐。那是我在世界上的安全和保护。即使在养老院，随着情况越来越糟，我也会拜访他，他会问我在做什么。我会告诉他新的演示，否则我会在广播中。这有点拯救了一切，因为我们有这个积极的事情要谈论。” </p><figure id="attachment_3844225" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3844225" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3844225" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="比利提名“ Metalhorse”专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3844225" class="wp-caption-text">比利提名“ Metalhorse”专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“ Metalhorse”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1。&#39;Metalhorse&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。“没什么值得获胜&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>3。“测试”</strong><br /> <strong>4。&#39;覆盖&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5。&#39;黑马朋友壮举。休·康威尔</strong><br /><strong>6。“生活不公平”</strong><br /> <strong>7。“计划”</strong><br /> <strong>8。“煤气”</strong><br /> <strong>9。“喜剧时机”</strong><br /> <strong>10。“奇怪的礼物”</strong><br /> <strong>11。“月亮爆炸”</strong></p><p> LP被描述为一张概念专辑，涉及有关生活的动荡 - 风险和愉悦，危险和振奋的主题。 “对我来说，&#39;Metalhorse&#39;是这个摇摇欲坠的游乐场，有些游乐设施很高兴上场，有些游乐设施不是。这就是生活一分钟的感觉，现在仍然有些感觉。”玛丽斯解释说。</p><p> She continued: “Those <a href="/artists/leonard-cohen">Leonard Cohen</a> days might be ahead of me.但是目前，即使不是真实的，也必须有一些希望。您必须告诉某人，这会没事的。”</p><p>在其他地方，比利的提名人士将在店内演出一系列专辑发行周以及本月晚些时候和四月的少数现场约会。在下面查看巡回演出的完整列表，然后访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbilly-nomates-tickets%2Fartist%2F5342572" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。</p><h2><strong>比利提名2025 Live和店​​内的巡回演出日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>6  - 法国巴黎的莱斯河畔节 - 独奏</strong><br /><strong>29  - 英国布里斯托尔的仪式联盟节标题 - 完整乐队</strong></p><p><strong>四月</strong><br /><strong>5  -  CRO CRO土地节标题，英国伦敦克罗伊登 - 独奏</strong></p><p><strong>五月（店内）</strong><br /> <strong>18  - 英国诺丁汉的粗糙贸易</strong><br /><strong>19  - 英国伦敦的粗糙贸易东部</strong><br /><strong>20  - 英国布莱顿居民</strong><br /><strong>22  - 英国考文垂刚赶到</strong></p><p>The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-nomates-announces-third-album-metalhorse-rebellious-new-single-the-test-3844195">Billy Nomates announces third album &#39;Metalhorse&#39; with rebellious new single &#39;The Test&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
